title: 1970s U.S.-Cuba Negotiations
description:
SEPTEMBER 8, 1994 | Mr. Kornbluh talked about an article on U.S.-Cuba relations during the 1970s written by Henry Kissinger which the National Security Archive was releasing for publication by New York Times Books. Various other persons knowledgeable on these relations also participated. 

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
